title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland-Alameda County Coliseum on 1989-12-31
description:
Set I
Sugar Magnolia >
Touch Of Grey >
Man Smart (Woman Smarter)
Big Boss Man *
Stuck Inside Of Mobile With The Memphis Blues Again
Shakedown Street
Set II
Midnight Countdown
Iko Iko
Victim Or The Crime >
Dark Star >
Drums >
Space >
Dear Mr. Fantasy >
Hey Jude >
Goin' Down The Road Feeling Bad >
Throwing Stones >
Not Fade Away

Encore:
Brokedown Palace
Sunshine Daydream
In The Midnight Hour
....
Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
Bonnie Raitt - Guitar *
